 valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">4.08</td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.69</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap></sec><sec><title>Efficacy on Severity and Conviction of Delusions</title><p>Levels of severity and conviction of delusions and their test statistics are shown in <bold>Table <xref ref-type="table" rid="T3">3</xref></bold>.</p><table-wrap id="T3" position="float"><label>Table 3</label><caption><p>Comparisons of severity and conviction of delusions across time points.</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5"><thead><tr><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Measures</th><th valign="top" align="center" colspan="4" rowspan="1">Wait-list condition<hr/></th><th valign="top" align="center" colspan="3" rowspan="1">Treatment condition<hr/></th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Overall change between pre-treatment, post-treatment, and follow-up assessments</th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><italic>Post hoc</italic> pairwise comparisons</th></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"/><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Baseline</th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Pre</th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Post</th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Follow-up</th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Pre</th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Post</th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Follow-up</th><th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Effect of time</th><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"/></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">PANSS positive</td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">19.81 (4.20)</td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">18.65 (5.27)</td><td valign="top"